Hey guys, I just uploaded part 1 of a parkour map called "Parkour School"!

vladthegreat100 recorded this over a month ago, so I thought that I would give it a try as well!

I hope you guys enjoy the video, and have a great day!

*Feedback is always appreciated!*

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOgehHHZ1A0

Step 1: Go to youtube, type: Minecraft Texture packs

Step 2: Go to te video.

Step 3: Click the adfly or Mediafire link or Drobox link......

Step 4: Download the texture pack

Step 5: Put that into your recycle bin

Step 6: Hit "Empty recycle bin"

Step 6: Enjoy your texture pack!
